{"tid":1854273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】油塘網店貨倉被偷2.5萬口罩 主要供應HKTVmall","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T11:48:48.000Z","uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24ea17401f19724b138a7fb43cebb6eb72b30df6","tid":1854273,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200131/large/1580470066_00b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200131%2Flarge%2F1580470066_00b5.jpg&h=3492259c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，全城一罩難求，本港近日發生多宗偷口罩事件。下午5時許，油塘四山街4號一樓一間網店職員報案，指其貨倉內半板貨不翼而飛，慌忙通知負責人及報案。經負責人羅小姐點算，證實損失25箱共2.5萬個口罩。警方到場調查，初步未見大門有撬毀痕迹，暫列盜竊案處理。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，負責人羅小姐於年三十時向泰國供應商訂購25箱口罩，每箱有20盒各50片口罩，貨物前日抵港，今日準備出貨給客戶。據知，該網店主要供應給HKTVmall，口罩售價大約80至100蚊元。"},{"pid":"cf39fa015e0210d6d25545fc36c012b7f80485d1","tid":1854273,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f00447b62f48f62a52f2e70b4759086b87e187b8","tid":1854273,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"25箱無車運唔走，要捉應該唔難"},{"pid":"9bcf42d86b6a13670fc1652662be69e915e09518","tid":1854273,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"仲好做過打劫金鋪，可以即刻轉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68650b62056d58eaf0ee472975a8392375156880","tid":1854273,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"即刻轉手30蚊5個都賺到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}